# Release Notes — v2

GCB v2 is the first release candidate of the Goldstonian Concordance Bible canonical index.

This release includes:
- the full 81-book structured canonical corpus
- foundational theological ontology
- foundational entity graph
- retrieval architecture
- media, transcript, and playlist architecture
- initial passage indexing
- benchmark harness
- export packaging

This release is intended for:
- open-source biblical infrastructure development
- LLM retrieval experiments
- theological knowledge graph construction
- Ethiopian canon discovery and comparison workflows